{% comment %}
  About Us Page Template
{% endcomment %}

<div class="section section--large">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h1>About PDlab Denture Repair</h1>
      <p class="section__subtitle">Your trusted partner in professional denture care</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <h2 class="card__title">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="card__content">
        Welcome to PDlab Denture Repair, your trusted partner for professional acrylic denture repair services by post. With years of experience in the dental industry, we understand how important your dentures are to your daily life, confidence, and overall well-being.
      </p>
      <p class="card__content">
        Founded with a mission to make quality denture repair accessible to everyone across the UK, we've developed a simple, secure postal service that brings professional denture care right to your doorstep. No appointments, no travel – just expert repairs delivered with care.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <h2 class="card__title">Why You Can Trust Us</h2>
      <div class="grid grid--2 mt-2">
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🎓 Certified Professionals</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            Our technicians hold industry-recognized certifications and undergo continuous training to stay current with the latest techniques and materials in denture repair.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🏆 Years of Experience</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            With over a decade of combined experience, our team has successfully repaired thousands of dentures, earning the trust of customers across the UK.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🔒 Secure & Insured</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            Every delivery is fully insured and tracked. We take the utmost care in handling your dentures from the moment they arrive until they're safely returned to you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">💎 Quality Guarantee</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            We stand behind our work with a 100% satisfaction guarantee. If you're not happy with the repair, we'll make it right or provide a full refund.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <h2 class="card__title">Our Commitment to You</h2>
      <p class="card__content" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <strong>Accessibility:</strong> We designed our service specifically for seniors and those who may find it difficult to visit a dental laboratory in person. Our website is easy to navigate, with large text and simple steps.
      </p>
      <p class="card__content" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <strong>Transparency:</strong> No hidden fees, no surprises. We provide clear pricing upfront and keep you informed at every stage of the repair process.
      </p>
      <p class="card__content" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <strong>Quality:</strong> We use only the highest quality materials and follow strict hygiene and safety protocols. Your health and satisfaction are our top priorities.
      </p>
      <p class="card__content" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <strong>Speed:</strong> We understand that being without your dentures can be difficult. That's why we offer fast turnaround times – most repairs are completed within 2-3 working days.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <h2 class="card__title">Our Certifications & Standards</h2>
      <p class="card__content">
        We are proud to maintain the highest standards in denture repair:
      </p>
      <ul style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 2; margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <li>Registered Dental Technicians with the General Dental Council (GDC)</li>
        <li>Full compliance with UK medical device regulations</li>
        <li>Certified infection control procedures</li>
        <li>Quality management system accreditation</li>
        <li>Fully insured for public liability and professional indemnity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <h2 class="card__title">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="grid grid--2 mt-2">
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary);">Compassion</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            We understand the emotional and practical challenges of denture problems. We treat every customer with empathy, respect, and care.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary);">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            We are committed to delivering the highest quality repairs using superior materials and expert craftsmanship.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary);">Integrity</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            We operate with honesty and transparency in all our dealings, from pricing to communication.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary);">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="card__content">
            We continuously improve our services and adopt new technologies to serve you better.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <h2 class="card__title">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <p class="card__content">
        Our team consists of experienced dental technicians who are passionate about helping people restore their smiles. Each member of our team brings specialized skills and a commitment to excellence.
      </p>
      <p class="card__content">
        We work as a close-knit family, dedicated to providing you with the best possible service. From the moment your dentures arrive at our laboratory to the moment they're returned to you, multiple team members ensure quality at every step.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-3">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Ready to Experience Our Service?</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        Join thousands of satisfied customers who trust us with their denture repairs.
      </p>
      <a href="/pages/services" class="btn btn--primary btn--large" style="margin-right: 1rem;">
        Get Started
      </a>
      <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn btn--secondary btn--large">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
